🎬 Netflix Clone

A simple Netflix-inspired web application built using React, JavaScript, HTML, and CSS. This project was created to practice React fundamentals, component-based development, and responsive web design.

🚀 Live Demo
https://cse-16-236-hc78uh349-anshita-garg.vercel.app/

🛠️ Tech Stack
- React
- JavaScript
- HTML5
- CSS3

✨ Features
- Netflix-style homepage
- Responsive design
- Reusable React components
- Movie cards with images
- Clean and modern UI

👩‍💻 Author
Anshita Garg

📌 Purpose
This project was built as a beginner-friendly React project to learn component-based UI development and modern frontend workflows.
